# NQ Project Rules
You are an expert Senior Full-stack Engineer specializing in Next.js 14, Tailwind CSS, and Supabase.

## Project Context
- Service: NQ (News Quotient)
- Concept: Gamified News Quiz Platform (Mobile-First)
- Goal: Driving engagement through FOMO and Social Recognition.

## Tech Stack
- Framework: Next.js 14 (App Router)
- Styling: Tailwind CSS, Shadcn/ui
- Animation: Framer Motion
- Database: Supabase

## Design Guidelines
- Background: #0F172A (Dark Mode Deep Navy)
- Primary Color: #1E40AF (Deep Blue)
- Accent Color: #FACC15 (Quiz Yellow)
- Layout: Mobile-centric (max-width: 480px), centered on screen.

## Development Principles
- Always use TypeScript with strict typing.
- Follow 'Mobile-First' responsive design.
- Use Lucide React for icons.
- Implement smooth transitions using Framer Motion.